docs.text: through a whole sequence of entirely probable events ( about as probable as hitting the lottery ) a large explosion takes place in the lincoln tunnel running under the hudson river in new york city .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: the explosion results in the tunnel collapsing at both ends , which causes not only massive loss of life , but traps a dozen people inside the wreckage of the tunnel .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: good old sly , who is only feet away from entering the tunnel when it collapses , offers his services to the rescuers , who gladly accept it .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: sly then enters the tunnel through a vent shaft ( think judge dredd ) which he can only go in , and not out off , and proceeds to try to rescue those trapped inside .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: so begins the fun , but the fun has to be quick , because this tunnel has started to spring a leak .
